episodes.title: Chapter 1
episodes.description: Assane Diop's life turns upside down when his father dies after being accused of a crime he didn't commit.

episodes.title: Chapter 2
episodes.description: Assane seeks revenge against Hubert Pellegrini, the wealthy man responsible for his father's downfall.

episodes.title: Chapter 3
episodes.description: Assane executes a heist inspired by Arsène Lupin, the fictional character his father loved.
